# Logs
# Root-only (a bare `logs` would also ignore source dirs named "logs", e.g. the
# session-log route under src/pages).
/logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

node_modules
dist
dist-ssr
*.local

